}}
票房大片寥寥无几、电影制作成本提升、观众减少、票价上升等因素共同导致美国电影业衰退，到1981年夏（六至九月）已持续一年多<ref name="NYTimesSupermanRelease">{{cite news | first = Pamela G. | last = Hollie | title = Hollywood Strategy For Summer Films | archive-date = 2021-05-23 | dead-url = no | date = 1981-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210523170107/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/26/business/hollywood-strategy-for-summer-films.html | website = The New York Times | access-date = 2021-07-10 | page = D1 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/26/business/hollywood-strategy-for-summer-films.html}}</ref>，业界预计年度票房要比上年减少2.5亿美元，降幅约一成<ref name="NYTimesPrediction">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Superman II' Predicted As Summer's Hit Movie | page = C11 | archive-date = 2021-05-23 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/05/25/movies/superman-ii-predicted-as-summer-s-hit-movie.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-05-25 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210523170108/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/05/25/movies/superman-ii-predicted-as-summer-s-hit-movie.html}}</ref>。制片厂急于推动下一部[[大片|大片]]问世，计划上映的电影比上一年还多，达六十余部。暑期是美国院线旺季，对12至24岁主观众群的行业竞争更加激烈<ref name="NYTimesSupermanRelease" /><ref name="NYTimesPrediction" />。

业界预计超级英雄续集电影《[[超人II|超人II]]》将统治1981年暑期档，专家和观众调查结果表明《[[帝国时代_(1981年电影)|帝国时代]]》、最新[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|詹姆斯·邦德系列电影]]《[[鐵金剛勇破海龍幫|鐵金剛勇破海龍幫]]》、《[[布偶的玩意|布偶的玩意]]》前景看好<ref name="NYTimesPrediction" />。相比之下，[[影院评分|影院评分]]投票数据表明期待乃至知道《夺宝奇兵》的观众很少，直到上映一周前的全国预映才改观<ref name="NYTimesPrediction" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Tis Almost The Season To Be Jolly, But Not Out in Hollywood | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/11/10/movies/tis-almost-the-season-to-be-jolly-but-not-out-in-hollywood.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-11-10 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411123344/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/11/10/movies/tis-almost-the-season-to-be-jolly-but-not-out-in-hollywood.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no | page = C7}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》发文称，为确保电影能在最好的位置和院线上映，派拉蒙向影院业主提出的条件比以往更优厚<ref name="NYTimesSupermanRelease" />。

电影新闻发布会耗费一万美元，出动骆驼两头、象一头、蟒蛇一条<ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Blake Edwards in Tiff Over 'S.O.B.' | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no | page = C17 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/25/movies/blake-edwards-in-tiff-over-sob.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120331/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/25/movies/blake-edwards-in-tiff-over-sob.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-06-25 | access-date = 2021-07-10}}</ref>。电影胶片装在铅封容器交给电影院以防篡改，其中附有写给影院经理的信，声称不当使用胶片将会问责。某影院看到信后告知派拉蒙，有人想盗取胶片制作[[盗版|盗版]]。<ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Jedi' Prints Stolen For Cassette Piracy, Movie Industry Says | archive-date = 2021-05-23 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/07/09/movies/jedi-prints-stolen-for-cassette-piracy-movie-industry-says.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1983-07-09 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | page = 11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210523170322/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/07/09/movies/jedi-prints-stolen-for-cassette-piracy-movie-industry-says.html}}</ref>派拉蒙为1200份胶片估计花费170万美元<ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Hollywood's Video Gamble | page = 640 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1982/03/28/magazine/hollywood-s-video-gamble.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1982-03-28 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411121830/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/03/28/magazine/hollywood-s-video-gamble.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
1981年6月12日，《夺宝奇兵》在美国和加拿大1078家电影院上映<ref>{{cite web | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark (1981) | archive-date = 2021-06-25 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-07-10 | publisher = [[The_Numbers|The Numbers]] | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Raiders-of-the-Lost-Ark#tab=summary | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210625181825/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Raiders-of-the-Lost-Ark#summary}}</ref><ref name="TheNumbersBOSummary">{{cite web | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark (1981) | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Raiders-of-the-Lost-Ark#tab=box-office | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-date = 2021-06-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210625181825/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Raiders-of-the-Lost-Ark#tab=box-office}}</ref>，周末进账830万美元，平均每家7705美元<ref name="NYTimesSupermanRelease" /><ref name="TheNumbers1981June12">{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for June 12, 1981 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/06/12 | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210604000701/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/06/12 | archive-date = 2021-06-04 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，领先同样新上映的《[[诸神之战_(1981年电影)|诸神之战]]》（660万美元）和《帝国时代》（490万美元）登上票房榜冠军宝座<ref name="TheNumbers1981June12" />。第二周电影收入800万美元排第三，跌幅仅四个百分点，落后新上映的《[[炮彈飛車|炮彈飛車]]》（1180万美元）和《超人II》（1410万美元）<ref>{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for June 19, 1981 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/06/19 | publisher = The Numbers | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121213556/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/06/19 | archive-date = 2021-01-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-07-10}}</ref>。《夺宝奇兵》第四周以730万美元爬到亚军位置，仅次于《超人II》（1090万美元）<ref>{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for June 26, 1981 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/06/26 | publisher = The Numbers | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227064956/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/06/26 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-date = 2021-02-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for July 3, 1981 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/07/03 | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-date = 2019-08-09 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190809224607/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/07/03}}</ref>，第六周以640万美元再度登顶<ref>{{cite web | title = Weekend Domestic Chart for July 17, 1981 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/07/17 | publisher = The Numbers | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210217144642/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-chart/weekend/1981/07/17 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-date = 2021-02-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。此后九周本片基本高居票房榜首位，在前十位停留四十周之久<ref name="TheNumbersBOSummary" />。九月初影片票房近1.25亿美元，排在1981年暑期电影首位，估计制片厂拿到的利润达7200万美元，减去卢卡斯和斯皮尔伯格的分成及市场宣传开支，派拉蒙还净赚2300万美元<ref name="NYTimesIndySummerWinner">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Hollywood Is Joyous Over Its Record Grossing Summer | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/09/09/movies/hollywood-is-joyous-over-its-record-grossing-summer.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-09-09 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | page = C25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309063502/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/09/09/movies/hollywood-is-joyous-over-its-record-grossing-summer.html | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

电影公映期间票房表现一直很好，上映半年后，业界高管笑称《夺宝奇兵》将是1981年圣诞大片<ref name="TelegraphRetro" /><ref name="NYTimesXmas">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Hollywood Shivers in a Crisis Of Confidence | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/20/movies/hollywood-shivers-in-a-crisis-of-confidence.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-12-20 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120318/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/20/movies/hollywood-shivers-in-a-crisis-of-confidence.html}}</ref>。影片至到1982年3月18日才正式下架，部分院线持续放映到七月<ref name="BOMTickets">{{cite web | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171025021920/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=raidersofthelostark.htm&adjust_yr=1&p=.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=raidersofthelostark.htm&adjust_yr=1&p=.htm | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-date = 2017-10-25}}</ref><ref name="EmpireOralHistoryPage5" /><ref name="Ginsberg">{{cite magazine | magazine = Daily Variety | date = 1982-07-20 | page = 1 | title = Spielberg King of B.O. Mountain | first = Steven | last = Ginsberg | location = Los Angeles}}</ref>，估计票房总额超2.12亿美元，远胜《[[金色池塘|金色池塘]]》（1.19亿美元）、《超人II》（1.08亿美元）、《[[杂牌军东征|杂牌军东征]]》（8530万美元）位居1981年电影首位<ref name="TheNumbersBOSummary" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Top 1981 Movies at the Domestic Box Office | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1981 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210519060145/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1981 | archive-date = 2021-05-19 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="OldGoodBOMSummary">{{cite web | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | access-date = 2018-12-13 | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=raidersofthelostark.htm | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181213083209/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=raidersofthelostark.htm | dead-url = yes | archive-date = 2018-12-13 }}</ref>。[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]估计本片共售出7700余万张电影票<ref name="BOMTickets" />。《夺宝奇兵》的本土总票房是最高周票房的27倍多，纪录保持至今<ref name="TelegraphRetro" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Leggiest Movies | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/legs/leggiest | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210519235408/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/legs/leggiest | archive-date = 2021-05-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

本片在美加两国以外市场进账约1.42亿美元，超越《鐵金剛勇破海龍幫》（1.41亿美元）和《超人II》（8220万美元）位居首位<ref name="TheNumbers1981OutsideNA">{{cite web | title = Top 1981 Movies at the International Box Office | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/international/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1981 | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191222023819/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/international/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1981 | archive-date = 2019-12-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。影片全球总票房3.54亿美元，是1981年世界电影票房冠军，远超亚军《鐵金剛勇破海龍幫》（1.95亿美元）和季军《超人II》（1.9亿美元）<ref name="TheNumbersBOSummary" /><ref name="TheNumbers1981OutsideNA" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Top 1981 Movies at the Worldwide Box Office | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/worldwide/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1981 | publisher = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210519060240/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/worldwide/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1981 | archive-date = 2021-05-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = 1981 Worldwide Box Office | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/world/1981/ | publisher = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210606224345/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/world/1981/ | archive-date = 2021-06-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《夺宝奇兵》多次重新发行，首先是1982年7月进账2140万美元，1983年3月又收入1140万美元<ref name="TelegraphRetro" /><ref name="Ginsberg" /><ref name="OldGoodBOMOveralls">{{cite web | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=releases&id=raidersofthelostark.htm | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | access-date = 2018-07-01 | archive-date = 2018-07-01 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701084038/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=releases&id=raidersofthelostark.htm }}</ref><ref name="NYTimesSummer1982">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = What Movies Will Be The Big Winners This Summer? | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no | page = C11 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1982/05/17/movies/what-movies-will-be-the-big-winners-this-summer.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-06-25 | access-date = 2021-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727181933/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/05/17/movies/what-movies-will-be-the-big-winners-this-summer.html }}</ref>。斯皮尔伯格监制的[[IMAX|IMAX]]修复版2012年在美国和加拿大267家影院上映，观众的热烈反响促使播映院线增至三百家<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-01-20 | dead-url = no | url = https://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/08/14/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-to-receive-imax-re-release/ | title = That's a Big Boulder, Indy: Steven Spielberg on the Imax Rerelease of 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' | last = Itzkoff | first = Dave | date = 2012-08-14 | website = The New York Times | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120032314/https://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/08/14/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-to-receive-imax-re-release }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Max | last = Nicholson | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark Extends Its IMAX Theatrical Run | website = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2012-09-14 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/14/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-extends-its-imax-theatrical-run | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131019104719/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/14/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-extends-its-imax-theatrical-run | archive-date = 2013-10-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' Run Extended | url = https://deadline.com/2012/09/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-run-extended-336429/ | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2012-09-14 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170621083314/http://deadline.com/2012/09/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-run-extended-336429/ | archive-date = 2017-06-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。电影的全球票房收入至此升至近3.9亿美元<ref name="OldGoodBOMSummary" />。

1981年北美暑期票房总额以19.5亿美元创下新纪录，比上年提升15.6%，售出的电影票增加22.5%，《夺宝奇兵》和《超人II》是其中最大的功臣<ref name="NYTimesIndySummerWinner" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Film Box Offices Set 8-Month Record | archive-date = 2021-04-10 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/10/08/movies/film-box-offices-set-8-month-record.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-10-08 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210410232114/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/10/08/movies/film-box-offices-set-8-month-record.html }}</ref>。这年最成功的电影主要向观众提供喜剧、趣味、逃避现实的途径<ref name="NYTimesIndySummerWinner" />，《超人II》打破多项票房纪录，但《夺宝奇兵》收入更高，在影院持续放映一年多<ref name="NYTimesSummer1982" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Star Trek II' Sets Mark For Sales at Opening | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no | page = C11 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1982/06/08/movies/star-trek-ii-sets-mark-for-sales-at-opening.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1982-06-08 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120317/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/06/08/movies/star-trek-ii-sets-mark-for-sales-at-opening.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Superman' Breaks Record | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/30/movies/superman-breaks-record.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-06-30 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-04-10 | dead-url = no | page = C5 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210410232117/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/30/movies/superman-breaks-record.html }}</ref>。《纽约时报》宣称，除非两部电影的票都卖完观众才会考虑其他作品<ref name="NYTimesQueue">{{cite news | first = Janet | last = Maslin | title = Film View; Unreal Heroes for the 80's | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/07/19/movies/film-view-unreal-heroes-for-the-80-s.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-07-19 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | page = 217 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727193720/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/07/19/movies/film-view-unreal-heroes-for-the-80-s.html | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《夺宝奇兵》还与《帝国反击战》、《[[大白鯊_(電影)|大白鲨]]》、《星球大战》占据历史电影票房四强高位，四部都是卢卡斯或斯皮尔伯格的作品<ref name="NYTimesSummer1982" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Chris | last = Chase | title = At The Movies; Lelouch film runs 3 hours; 6 if you'd like. | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1982/06/11/movies/at-the-movies-lelouch-film-runs-3-hours-6-if-you-d-like.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1982-06-11 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | page = C10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120318/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/06/11/movies/at-the-movies-lelouch-film-runs-3-hours-6-if-you-d-like.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="NYTimesOscarNom">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Reds' And 'Golden Pond' Top Oscar Nominations | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1982/02/12/movies/reds-and-golden-pond-top-oscar-nominations.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1982-02-12 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | page = C20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201014065237/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/02/12/movies/reds-and-golden-pond-top-oscar-nominations.html | archive-date = 2020-10-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
《夺宝奇兵》赢得评论家和观众普遍好评<ref name="AVClubRetro" /><ref name="TelegraphRetro" />，[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會]]与影评人[[文森特·坎比|文森特·坎比]]都把本片列入1981年十大佳片<ref>{{cite news | title = Film Board Picks 'bests' | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/17/movies/film-board-picks-bests.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-12-17 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no | page = C32 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120322/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/17/movies/film-board-picks-bests.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Vincent | last = Canby | title = Film View; For American Movies, A Minor Renaissance | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/27/movies/film-view-for-american-movies-a-minor-renaissance.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-12-27 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411123349/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/27/movies/film-view-for-american-movies-a-minor-renaissance.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>。坎比称赞影片堪称经典，是美国电影史上极具格调和幽默的杰作，把过去的系列电影去芜存菁，为现代观众留下最完美的电影模式<ref name="NYTimesCanbyReview" />。[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]赞扬本片与儿时的漫画书和电影相比青出于蓝胜于蓝，呈现一连串“令人屏气凝神的奇妙历险”。在他看来，电影的娱乐效果无懈可击，以《星球大战》、[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|詹姆斯·邦德系列电影]]、《超人》的格局营造冒险史诗。<ref name="RevEbert">{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | author-link = 罗杰·埃伯特 | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-1981 | website = RogerEbert.com | date = 1981-01-01 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-06-04 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210604230652/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-1981}}</ref>亚瑟·奈特在《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》发文，称持续不断的刺激场面令电影节奏稳定<ref name="ReviewTHR">{{cite web | first = Arthur | last = Knight | title = 'Raiders of the Lost Ark': THR's 1981 Review | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/raiders-lost-ark-review-1981-movie-1011481/ | website = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 1981-06-05 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-07-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210704113757/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/raiders-lost-ark-review-1981-movie-1011481/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》刊登斯蒂芬·克莱恩的文章，认为电影对想逃脱现实的观众而言非常振奋，娱乐效果十足，他还称赞电影在动作、喜剧，以及神秘神话的悬念间完美平衡<ref name="VarietyReview" />。[[迈克尔·斯拉格|迈克尔·斯拉格]]把《夺宝奇兵》称为“终极周六动作日场”<ref name="RollingStoneReview">{{cite web | last = Sragow | first = Michael | title = Inside 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' | website = [[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] | date = 1981-06-25 | archive-date = 2021-06-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210603230220/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/inside-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-69261/ | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/inside-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-69261/ | access-date = 2021-07-11}}</ref>。[[吉恩·西斯克尔|吉恩·西斯克尔]]认为影片的娱乐程度已达“商业片”极致，正是这类作品让子孙后代对电影艺术兴奋不已<ref name="GeneSiskelReview">{{cite web | first = Gene | last = Siskel | title = The Movie Reviews | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1999-10-15-9910200025-story.html | website = Chicago Tribune | date = 1999-10-15 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210704114235/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1999-10-15-9910200025-story.html | archive-date = 2021-07-04 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。
[[File:Paul_Freeman.jpg|thumb]]（摄于2016年）]] 

[[理查德·西克尔|理查德·西克尔]]称《夺宝奇兵》是斯皮尔伯格回归之作，是《大白鲨》后对他才华的完整体现<ref name="timeSlambangPage1" />，如果[[華特·迪士尼|華特·迪士尼]]还在世肯定也会拍，把幻想与过场动画“引人入胜”地结合起来<ref name="timeSlambangPage5" />。[[斯坦利·考夫曼|斯坦利·考夫曼]]自称对电影的惊悚场面毫不感冒，频繁高得令人厌烦。他批评本片缺乏创新，只管依赖怀旧、翻新老片<ref name="NewRepublicReview">{{cite web | first = Stanley | last = Kauffmann | title = Old Ark, New Covenant | url = https://newrepublic.com/article/134104/old-ark-new-covenant | website = The New Republic | date = 1981-07-04 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-06-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210605020621/https://newrepublic.com/article/134104/old-ark-new-covenant}}</ref>。[[宝琳·凯尔|宝琳·凯尔]]批评卢卡斯与斯皮尔伯格专为经济利益拍摄本片，立足点就像销售人员一样只想吸引最广泛的受众。《夺宝奇兵》翻新老系列电影后内容足够复杂，并以巧妙剪辑避免陈词滥调，但过分注重超越昔日电影的华丽动作场面，对人物塑造和情节进展不利。在她看来，斯皮尔伯格经历《一九四一》的失败后过于谨慎，许多桥段证明他只是仓促而为，不再像以往那般精益求精。<ref name="PaulineKael">{{cite web  | first = Pauline | last = Kael | title = Whipped | url = https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/1981/06/15/whipped | website = [[紐約客|The New Yorker]] | date = 1981-06-15 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-07-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210703173611/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/1981/06/15/whipped}}</ref><ref name="PaulineKaelNYT">{{cite news | date = 2001-09-04 | first = Lawrence | last = Van Gelder | title = Pauline Kael, Provocative and Widely Imitated New Yorker Film Critic, Dies at 82 | website = The New York Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210623133639/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/09/04/movies/pauline-kael-provocative-and-widely-imitated-new-yorker-film-critic-dies-at-82.html | archive-date = 2021-06-23 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2001/09/04/movies/pauline-kael-provocative-and-widely-imitated-new-yorker-film-critic-dies-at-82.html | access-date = 2021-07-11}}</ref>卢卡斯后为1988年奇幻片《[[风云际会_(电影)|风云际会]]》的反派起名凯尔<ref name="PaulineKaelNYT" />。[[戴夫·科尔|戴夫·科尔]]认为，电影剧情都是仓促辗转各地，令人感觉单调。他还批评片中英雄多次为抢夺约柜放弃爱情，观众恐怕无法认同。<ref>{{cite web | first = Dave | last = Kehr | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | url = https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/raiders-of-the-lost-ark/Film?oid=4817691 | website = Chicago Reader | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-06-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210605020753/https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/raiders-of-the-lost-ark/Film?oid=4817691}}</ref>

主要演员的演出普受好评，埃伯特认为充满乐趣和不寻常的人物令本片升华，不局限于杰出技术成就。在他看来，福特塑造的人物沉默而固执，仿佛《碧血金沙》里的亨弗莱·鲍嘉增加自嘲能力。<ref name="RevEbert" />克莱恩称赞福特演出引人入胜，堪称职业生涯重要亮点<ref name="VarietyReview" />。坎比称福特和阿兰塑造的人物都很坚韧，令人倍感亲切<ref name="NYTimesCanbyReview" />。埃伯特称赞阿兰饰演的玛丽昂坚韧中充满魅力<ref name="RevEbert" />，奈特赞扬片中男明星身陷危机时，玛丽昂依然智商在线。在他看来，玛丽昂堪称[[女性主義|女权]]表率。<ref name="ReviewTHR" />斯拉格声称，阿兰的身体素质丝毫不输福特，她活力十足，对福特呆若木鸡的演出形成良好补充<ref name="RollingStoneReview" />。凯尔批评大部分演员表现生硬，一板一眼地照本宣科，但特别称赞弗里曼在苍蝇爬进嘴后继续演出<ref name="PaulineKael" />，弗里曼笑称这是对他职业生涯最好的评价<ref name="EmpireOralHistoryPage3" />。克莱恩认为托赫特是二战后银幕上最咄咄逼人的纳粹模式化形象，但对里斯-戴维斯与艾略特的演出青眼有加<ref name="VarietyReview" />。

许多影评人称赞打开约柜桥段特效表现优异<ref name="VarietyReview" /><ref name="NYTimesCanbyReview" /><ref name="ReviewTHR" />。奈特就称本片特效师理应获特别奖<ref name="ReviewTHR" />，坎比认为片中特效如同斯皮尔伯格作品《[[第三類接觸_(電影)|第三类接触]]》的结局般令人眼花缭乱<ref name="NYTimesCanbyReview" />。埃伯特自称在本片看到最精彩的卡车追逐戏，比《[[布利特_(电影)|布利特]]》（1968年）或《[[霹靂神探|霹靂神探]]》（1971年）更出色<ref name="RevEbert" />。[[阿尔让·哈梅茨|阿尔让·哈梅茨]]、克莱恩、西克尔认为，片中有那么多人物死亡，那么多恐怖场面，评为任何孩童无需成人陪同就能观看的PG级实在太放水。介于PG级和R级之间的PG-13级是在1984年诞生，要求13岁以下儿童需成人陪同观看，一定程度上就是因为这年上映的本片前传《魔宮傳奇》，据称还有儿童看过该片后夜里做噩梦。<ref name="VarietyReview" /><ref name="GeneSiskelReview" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Raiders': Too Terrifying To Be PG? | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/16/movies/raiders-too-terrifying-to-be-pg.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-06-16 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | page = C7 | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120327/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/16/movies/raiders-too-terrifying-to-be-pg.html | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = PG-13 at 20: How 'Indiana' remade films | url = https://www.today.com/popculture/pg-13-20-how-indiana-remade-films-wbna5798549 | website = [[今天_(NBC)|Today]] | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 2004-08-23 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210605020619/https://www.today.com/popculture/pg-13-20-how-indiana-remade-films-wbna5798549 | archive-date = 2021-06-05 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

