lberg and Harrison Ford come swashbuckling back into the awards fight? | website = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 2008-05-08 | access-date = 2018-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180620153230/https://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/05/will-indiana-jo.html | archive-date = 2018-06-20 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

== 周边商品 ==
=== 家用传媒 ===
家用[[錄影機|錄影機]]市场在20世纪80年代初迅速发展，过去[[家用录像系统|VHS]]录像带营收尚不入片商法眼，但1983年局面大变，录像带收入最高可达电影总收益的13%，单北美洲录像带版权收入就有50万美元<ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | archivedate = 2021-04-25 | deadurl = no | date = 1984-05-17 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/07/movies/hollywood-thriving-on-video-cassette-boom.html | title = Hollywood Thriving On Video-cassette Boom | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2021-07-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210425180848/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/07/movies/hollywood-thriving-on-video-cassette-boom.html | page = A1 }}</ref>。1983年11月，派拉蒙推出创纪录的50万本《夺宝奇兵》家用录像带，39.95美元单价远低于竞争对手，希望扩大受众面，推动家用录像机普及<ref>{{cite news | first = Sandra | last = Salmans | title = Hollywood Gambles On Video | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210206093026/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/12/12/business/hollywood-gambles-on-video.html | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1983/12/12/business/hollywood-gambles-on-video.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1983-12-12 | archive-date = 2021-02-06 | dead-url = no | page = D1 }}</ref>。1985年9月，本片已售出上百万本录像带，刷新畅销VHS录像带纪录<ref>{{cite news | title = 'Beverly Hills Cop' To Be a Video Cassette | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1985/09/13/movies/beverly-hills-cop-to-be-a-video-cassette.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1985-09-13 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | page = C26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226173820/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/09/13/movies/beverly-hills-cop-to-be-a-video-cassette.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1991年，[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]发动号称“至今……最大规模的录像带促销活动”，印第安纳·琼斯三部曲的录像带均以5.99美元单价在麦当劳餐厅销售。此时三部电影一共已售出上千万本录像带，预计麦当劳的促销还能再卖五百万<ref>{{cite news | author = Billboard | title = $5.99 McDeal on 'Indiana Jones' Videos | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1991-12-07-9104200174-story.html | website = Chicago Tribune | date = 1991-12-07 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201215041721/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1991-12-07-9104200174-story.html | archive-date = 2020-12-15 }}</ref>。为与印第安纳·琼斯系列的其他作品一致，2000年时本片的宣传片名已改成《印第安纳·琼斯之夺宝奇兵》<ref name="EbertTitle" />。

印第安纳·琼斯三部曲2003年捆绑发布[[DVD|DVD]]套装，销售火爆一如录像带，卖出上百万份而且创下DVD套装销售速度新纪录。套装新增两小时的纪录片，其中包括三部曲的拍摄经历、删除镜头、幕后花絮等<ref>{{cite web | title = Indiana Jones 'raids DVD record' | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3229887.stm | publisher = BBC News Online | date = 2003-10-31 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-07-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210707081606/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3229887.stm }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Keith | last = Phipps | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | access-date = 2021-07-11 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.avclub.com/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-1798199027 | website = The A.V. Club | date = 2003-10-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191115100120/https://film.avclub.com/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-1798199027 | archive-date = 2019-11-15 }}</ref><ref name="IGNBluRay2012">{{cite web | first = RL | last = Shaffer | title = Indiana Jones: The Complete Adventures Blu-ray Review | archive-date = 2018-09-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180916052642/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/14/indiana-jones-the-complete-adventures-blu-ray-review-2 | website = IGN | date = 2012-09-14 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/14/indiana-jones-the-complete-adventures-blu-ray-review-2 }}</ref>。2012年，印第安纳·琼斯四部曲推出[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]收藏版《印第安纳·琼斯：完整探险》，斯皮尔伯格亲自参与修复，提升几部电影的视听品质<ref name="IGNBluRay2012" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Borys | last = Kit | title = 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' to Get Imax Rerelease | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-07-11 | date = 2012-08-14 | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/raiders-lost-ark-imax-361878/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126094756/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/raiders-lost-ark-imax-361878 | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ColliderBluRay2012">{{cite web | first = Andre | last = Dellamorte | title = Indiana Jones: The Complete Adventures Blu-ray Review | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://collider.com/indiana-jones-blu-ray-review/ | publisher = [[Collider|Collider]] | date = 2012-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200109143223/https://collider.com/indiana-jones-blu-ray-review/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-01-09 }}</ref>，其中包含以往家用传媒附带的额外内容<ref name="ColliderBluRay2012" />。2021年是《夺宝奇兵》上映四十周年，印第安纳·琼斯四部曲发布修复版[[4K解析度|4K解析度]][[超高畫質電視|超高画质]]蓝光影碟套装，片源是电影原版胶片<ref>{{cite web | first = Chris | last = Reed | title = Indiana Jones Box Set 4K UHD Blu-Ray Preorders Down to $79.99 | date = 2021-03-16 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/indiana-jones-box-set-4k-uhd-blu-ray-is-up-for-preorder | website = IGN | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510030723/https://www.ign.com/articles/indiana-jones-box-set-4k-uhd-blu-ray-is-up-for-preorder | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

