== 主题分析 ==
=== 否定纳粹 ===
[[File:Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-P049500,_Berlin,_Aufmarsch_der_SA_in_Spandau.jpg|thumb]]街头。《夺宝奇兵》可以理解成犹太人的报复，展现天神否定纳粹]]

《夺宝奇兵》可以理解成犹太人幻想借天神之手惩处发动[[納粹大屠殺|大屠杀]]的纳粹<ref name="ebertGreatest" />。斯皮尔伯格是犹太人，传说约柜是天神传给犹太人的[[十誡|十誡]]容器<ref name="ebertGreatest" /><ref name="Cinephilia" />。据《圣经》记载，约柜是镀金的木箱，而且非常神圣，人体不能接触，只能用杆子抬<ref name="EmpireMacGuffins" />。纳粹政权因信仰迫害犹太人，但却需要犹太神器来征服世界。神器是如此神圣，纳粹不但无法接触，连他们印在运输箱上的符号也被抹去，箱子完好无损，以此体现约柜否定纳粹。影片最后，胆敢打开约柜的纳粹势力无一幸免。<ref name="ebertGreatest" /><ref name="Cinephilia" />约柜释放神圣的力量制止纳粹，感知危险的主角毫发无损<ref name="AVClub1981">{{cite web | first = Tom | last = Breihan | title = Did 1981 belong to Mad Max, Indiana Jones, or Snake Plissken? | url = https://www.avclub.com/did-1981-belong-to-mad-max-indiana-jones-or-snake-pli-1798250059 | website = The A.V. Club | date = 2016-07-29 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108102421/https://film.avclub.com/did-1981-belong-to-mad-max-indiana-jones-or-snake-pli-1798250059 | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

琼斯掉在行驶卡车上时，发动机盖上的奔驰商标一闪而过，嘲笑当年奔驰公司助纣为虐、协助纳粹<ref name="ebertGreatest" /><ref>{{cite news | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-06-12-mn-7400-story.html | title = Daimler-Benz to Pay $12 Million for War Forced Labor | agency = Times Wire Services | date = 1988-06-12 | website = Los Angeles Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224204051/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-06-12-mn-7400-story.html}}</ref>。伊丽莎白·赫希曼认为片中包含[[形上學|形上學]]元素，约柜作为[[犹太教－基督教|犹太教－基督教]]神话圣物，拥有极其重要的宗教意义，主角的标准英雄任务对此黯然失色。天神注定代表善，摧毁纳粹反派可比[[雅威|雅威]]目睹[[十灾|十灾]]降临奴役[[以色列人|以色列人]]的古埃及。<ref>{{cite journal | first = Elizabeth | last = Hirschman | title = Legends in Our Own Time: How Motion Pictures And Television Shows Fulfill The Functions Of Myth | journal = The American Journal of Semiotics | publisher = Philosophy Documentation Center | volume = 17 | issue = 3 | pages = 7-9, 12-46 | date = Fall 2001 | location = Charlottesville, Virginia | doi = 10.5840/ajs200117329 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://www.proquest.com/docview/213749767 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121032637/https://www.proquest.com/docview/213749767 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 影史致敬与怀旧 ===
《夺宝奇兵》从侧面反映电影变迁，受到许多电影启发，包含大量电影隐喻，导演明确表示本片以电影为核心，旨在致敬电影制作<ref>{{cite web | last = Schickel | first = Richard | title = Cinema: Slam! Bang! A Movie Movie (Page 3) | url = http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,949205-3,00.html | website = Time | access-date = 2021-07-11 | date = 1981-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210505123352/http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,949205-3,00.html | archive-date = 2021-05-05 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。影片直接从二十世纪上半叶的系列电影汲取灵感<ref name="Cinephilia" /><ref name="MovieFone" /><ref name="GRAdarOverview" /><ref name="timeSlambangPage1" />，还有指向《[[公民凯恩|公民凯恩]]》（1941年）、《[[死吻|死吻]]》（1955年）、《[[大鏢客|大鏢客]]》（1961年）、《[[阿拉伯的劳伦斯_(电影)|阿拉伯的劳伦斯]]》（1962年）等电影的情节<ref name="NYTimesCanbyReview" /><ref name="FSRHomage">{{cite web | first = H. Perry | last = Horton | title = Unearthing History: The Visual Echoes of 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' | url = https://filmschoolrejects.com/unearthing-history-visual-echoes-raiders-lost-ark/ | publisher = Film School Rejects | date = 2017-08-18 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210613045710/https://filmschoolrejects.com/unearthing-history-visual-echoes-raiders-lost-ark/ | archive-date = 2021-06-13 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。约柜最后放在巨大的仓库里，与《公民凯恩》主人翁儿时心爱的雪橇命运类似<ref name="NYTimesCanbyReview" /><ref name="McGee2011">{{cite web | title = Citizen Kane (1941) | first = Scott | last = McGee | publisher = [[特纳经典电影频道|Turner Classic Movies]] | date = 2011-08-12 | access-date = 2020-08-07 | url = http://www.tcm.com/this-month/article/71645%7C0/Pop-Culture.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807003841/http://www.tcm.com/this-month/article/71645%7C0/Pop-Culture.html | archive-date = 2020-08-07 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。《夺宝奇兵》还有许多指向卢卡斯电影的隐喻：德国潜艇传出的信号意为“1138”，隐喻科幻片《[[500年后|500年后]]》，灵魂之井有代表[[R2-D2|R2-D2]]和[[C-3PO|C-3PO]]的象形文字<ref name="Cinephilia" /><ref name="MovieFone" />。理查德·克林克利指出，许多观众看到《[[大衛王_(電影)|大卫王]]》（1985年）里的约柜时只会想到《夺宝奇兵》而非《圣经》记载，在他看来，这是电影视觉传媒影响文化传播的有力证明，接受视觉传媒而非传统文本教育的人越来越多<ref>{{cite journal | first = Richmond | last = Crinkley | title = The Ark of the Cinemate | journal = Film Comment | publisher = Film at Lincoln Center | volume = 21 | issue = 4 | date = July–August 1985 | location = New York City | url = https://www.proquest.com/docview/210241430 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | pages = 76–77 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121025244/https://www.proquest.com/docview/210241430 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《夺宝奇兵》与同年的《超人II》一样包含美国安全面临威胁的主题。两部电影都是美国时代的象征，代表此时美国公民的恐惧。纳粹人物以过去威胁美国的势力为原型，《夺宝奇兵》就像《超人II》一样，幻想超出人类的强大力量介入，防止敌对势力破坏，对这样的英雄观众只能欣赏、永远都无法效仿。珍妮特·马斯林指出，此类电影幻想与超凡脱俗的人物旨在满足观众心理，他们无意反思周围的世界。<ref name="NYTimesQueue" />琼斯竭力夺回约柜不但是为阻止纳粹，也是为个人荣耀。如果纳粹实现目标创造所向披靡的军队，全世界无数普通人的生活将发生巨变，但电影对此完全没有涉足。<ref name="NYTimesQueue" />

美国人的民族自豪感因惨淡收场的[[越南战争|越南战争]]（1955至1975年）、[[水门事件|水门事件]]政治丑闻（1972年）、20世纪80年代初的经济衰退、其他国家的影响越来越大等因素陷入低谷，《夺宝奇兵》可以视为对这等消极情绪的积极反击<ref name="AVClubRetro" /><ref name="Hunter-2003">{{cite journal | first = Latham | last = Hunter | title = The Celluloid Cubicle: Regressive Constructions of Masculinity in 1990s Office Movies | journal = The Journal of American Culture | publisher = Wiley-Blackwell | volume = 26 | issue = 1 | pages = 71–86 | date = 2003-03 | location = Hoboken, New Jersey | doi = 10.1111/1542-734X.00075 | url = https://www.proquest.com/docview/200624872 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121025235/https://www.proquest.com/docview/200624872 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。对于观众来说，电影的时代背景带有浪漫怀旧色彩并充满冒险机遇<ref name="NYTimesSerials" /><ref name="AVClubRetro" />。罗宾·伍德认为本片与《超人》、《星球大战》异曲同工，都可视为老系列电影的衍生作品，观众能从中收获熟悉、易于接受的内容，呈现旧传统价值观的理想愿景。在他看来，此举旨在平息当时激进社会运动对变革的渴望。<ref>{{cite journal | first = Matt | last = Yockey | title = Somewhere in Time: Utopia and the Return of Superman | journal = The Velvet Light Trap | publisher = University of Texas Press | issue = 61 | pages = 32–33 |  date = Spring 2008 | volume = 61 | location = Austin, Texas | doi = 10.1353/vlt.2008.0007 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506121321/https://search.proquest.com/docview/222840506 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.proquest.com/docview/222840506 | access-date = 2021-07-07 | archive-date = 2021-05-06}}</ref>詹妮弗·巴克认为，《夺宝奇兵》不过迎合观众心愿，无意挑战他们漏洞百出的价值观和信仰<ref name="Barker-2008">{{cite journal | first = Jennifer | last = Barker | title = 'A Hero Will Rise': The Myth of the Fascist Man in Fight Club and Gladiator | journal = Literature/Film Quarterly | publisher = Salisbury University | volume = 36 | issue = 3 | year = 2008 | location = Salisbury, Maryland | url = https://www.proquest.com/docview/226986979 | page = 173 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121025243/https://www.proquest.com/docview/226986979 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 男子气概与殖民主义 ===
琼斯代表本片所在时代充满男子气概的动作英雄原型，可以视为在女权思想日益增强之时重新强调传统男子气概。莱瑟姆·亨特指出，《夺宝奇兵》、《[[轰天炮|轰天炮]]》（1987年）、《[[終極警探|終極警探]]》（1988年）都是普通人排除万难，以此促进美国实力。<ref name="Hunter-2003" />身为美国英雄，琼斯不情不愿地担负起拯救世界重任，战胜的对手几乎全是外国人<ref name="AVClubRetro" /><ref name="TelegraphRetro" />。巴克认为琼斯信奉个人价值，与法西斯或极权统治对抗，所以本片属于“保守系列奇幻片”<ref name="Barker-2008" />。亨特认为影片注重男子气概未免鼠目寸光，电影靠帮观众逃避现实热卖，呈现的英雄出类拔萃，反映观众自身的无力感<ref name="Hunter-2003" />。

评论家批评琼斯的考古学家形象根本不够格，所作所为等同于盗窃<ref name="McGeough-2006">{{cite journal | first = Kevin | last = McGeough | title = Heroes, Mummies, and Treasure: Near Eastern Archaeology in the Movies | journal = Near Eastern Archaeology | publisher = University of Chicago Press | volume = 68 | issue = 3/4 | date = September–December 2006 | location = Chicago, Illinois | doi = 10.1086/NEA25067670 | url = https://www.proquest.com/docview/221537348 | access-date = 2021-04-10 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121032726/https://www.proquest.com/docview/221537348 | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|174–177}}。考古学家温尼弗雷德·克里默认为琼斯“行为介于考古学家和专业盗墓者之间”，堪称“考古学界最恶劣的一员”<ref>{{cite web | first = Christopher | last = Joyce | title = Indiana Jones: Saving History or Stealing It? | url = https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=89724552&t=1598133427554 | publisher = [[全国公共广播电台|NPR]] | date = 2008-04-21 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2020-08-22 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200822222138/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=89724552&t=1598133427554}}</ref>。凯文·麦克乔夫撰文指出，老电影从来不让考古学家当英雄，他们通常是由真正的英雄拯救或征服。琼斯在独立自主和身体强壮程度上达到传统英雄标准，但广为人知的聪慧头脑令他与昔日英雄拉开距离。<ref name="McGeough-2006" />{{rp|174–177}}琼斯追踪约柜一定程度上是为个人荣誉，他有机会摧毁约柜、避免被纳粹利用，但贝洛克看出他只是虚张声势，琼斯只能妥协。贝洛克自认就像心理扭曲的琼斯，两者区别很小。<ref name="AVClub1981" /><ref name="McGeough-2006" />{{rp|178}}

塔蒂亚娜·普罗科娃认为《夺宝奇兵》充满[[殖民主义|殖民主义]]色彩，琼斯和纳粹都是侵略属于有色人种领土的白人男子，为私利窃取当地宝藏<ref name="Prorokova-2020">{{cite book | last = Prorokova | first = Tatiana | editor = Randy Laist | date = 2020-04-03 | title = Excavating Indiana Jones: Essays on the Films and Franchise | chapter = Translocations, Cultural Geography and Anthropological Imperialism in Raiders of the Lost Ark | location = Jefferson, North Carolina | publisher = [[麥克法蘭公司|McFarland & Company]] | isbn = 9781476639727 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=lOnaDwAAQBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121031153/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=lOnaDwAAQBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|51–52, 56–57}}。琼斯把约柜的超自然力量连同文化意义一起否定，把它变成自己收集的奖品<ref name="Prorokova-2020" />{{rp|58–59}}。身为英雄，他代表美国保护约柜免受他人染指的权利不受约束。他的名字源于美国印第安纳州，该州又因殖民者与印第安人交战得名。<ref name="Prorokova-2020" />{{rp|57}}全世界大部分地区在《夺宝奇兵》的背景时代都由殖民者统治，片中人物只要不是白人，要么被纳粹征服，要么依赖美国白人救助，要么就与纳粹合作<ref name="Prorokova-2020" />{{rp|56}}。

== 影响 ==
《夺宝奇兵》对流行文化的影响经久不衰，有现代电影试金石之称，创造的电影框架至今仍由其他电影效仿<ref name="EmpireOralHistoryPage5" /><ref name="DOGLegacy">{{cite web | first = Kayti | last = Burt | title = How Raiders of the Lost Ark Continues to Influence Pop Culture | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/how-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-continues-to-influence-pop-culture/ | publisher = Den of Geek | date = 2019-06-13 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709182856/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/how-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-continues-to-influence-pop-culture/ | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。斯皮尔伯格表示，这是他眼中印第安纳·琼斯系列最完美的作品，他无意变更其中任何内容<ref name="EmpireOralHistoryPage5" />。

福特接下来获选出演1982年科幻[[邪典追捧|邪典经典]]电影《[[银翼杀手|银翼杀手]]》<ref name="TelegraphRetro" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Stephen | last = Dalton | title = Blade Runner: anatomy of a classic | url = https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/news-bfi/features/blade-runner | date = 2019-04-25 | publisher = British Film Institute | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-05-19 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210519123034/https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/news-bfi/features/blade-runner}}</ref>，卡斯丹变成好莱坞灸手可热的编剧，协助卢卡斯创作《星球大战》续集《帝国反击战》<ref name="Cinephilia" /><ref name="NYTimesIndySummerWinner" />。阿兰对本片颇感失望，她希望玛丽昂主要是因为父亲、因为她对约柜的执念参与其中，而非现在这样因为经济利益和与琼斯的感情。她建议改写人物情节，深入发展角色，但都沦为空谷足音。<ref name="Cinephilia" /><ref name="WAPOAllen" />不过，阿兰对各年龄段女子受玛丽昂启发颇感兴奋，据她透露，电影上映40年后她还收到青少年女子的积极反馈<ref name="40thannTHR" />。[[斯坦利·雷德|斯坦利·雷德]]与[[罗伯特·劳伦斯·库恩|罗伯特·劳伦斯·库恩]]在本片上映后不久起诉电影主创，要求赔偿2.1亿美元，声称电影是根据库恩所创剧本和尚未出版的小说《约柜》改编，但案件结果至今不明<ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Suit On 'ark' Charges Stealing From A Novel | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/07/09/movies/suit-on-ark-charges-stealing-from-a-novel.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-07-09 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | page = C20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210410232136/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/07/09/movies/suit-on-ark-charges-stealing-from-a-novel.html | archive-date = 2021-04-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

本片促使更多学生投身考古学研究，许多现代考古学家声称影片令他们深受启发。里斯-戴维斯自称曾有150余名讲师、教授、考古学家向他表示，正是看过《夺宝奇兵》后才对考古学感兴趣。<ref name="NatGeo" />电影拍完后，印第安纳·琼斯原版帽子和外套随意丢在卢卡斯的[[天行者牧场|天行者牧场]]，直到2012年戴博拉·纳杜尔曼·兰迪斯找到后开始在伦敦[[维多利亚和阿尔伯特博物馆|维多利亚和阿尔伯特博物馆]]举办的好莱坞服装展上展出<ref name="TheRinger" />。

=== 文化影响 ===
[[File:Indy_and_Marion.jpg|thumb]]]]

1999年，《夺宝奇兵》因“文化、历史和美学领域的显著成就”入选[[國會圖書館_(美國)|美国国会图书馆]][[國家影片登記表|國家影片登記表]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Complete National Film Registry Listing | url = https://www.loc.gov/programs/national-film-preservation-board/film-registry/complete-national-film-registry-listing/ | publisher = [[國會圖書館_(美國)|Library of Congress]] | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210625061213/https://www.loc.gov/programs/national-film-preservation-board/film-registry/complete-national-film-registry-listing/ | archive-date = 2021-06-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Jamie | last = Allen | title = U.S. film registry adds 25 new titles | url = http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/Movies/9911/16/natl.film.registry/ | publisher = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | date = 1999-11-16 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210703174505/http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/Movies/9911/16/natl.film.registry/ | archive-date = 2021-07-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。1997年[[伯纳德·温劳布|伯纳德·温劳布]]在评价本片影响时指出，“观众普遍……是从《夺宝奇兵》开始对传统的家庭G级片失去兴趣”，“不管这纯属偶然还是有意为之，电影人拍出的动作片高潮迭起，对成年观众极具吸引力，同时也能得到儿童观众认可”<ref>{{cite news | first = Bernard | last = Weinraub | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1997/07/22/movies/movies-for-children-and-their-parents-are-far-from-pollyanna.html | title = Movies for Children, and Their Parents, Are Far From 'Pollyanna' | date = 1997-07-22 | website = The New York Times  | access-date = 2021-07-11 | page = C9 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200908061359/https://www.nytimes.com/1997/07/22/movies/movies-for-children-and-their-parents-are-far-from-pollyanna.html | archive-date = 2020-09-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。多次与卢卡斯合作的[[加里·库尔茨|加里·库尔茨]]表示，《夺宝奇兵》堪称卢卡斯事业的转折点，令他确信观众对“过山车般的历险”兴趣更胜情节<ref>{{cite web | first = Ken | last = P. | title = An Interview with Gary Kurtz | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2002/11/11/an-interview-with-gary-kurtz | website = IGN | date = 2002-11-11 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506132129/https://www.ign.com/articles/2002/11/11/an-interview-with-gary-kurtz | archive-date = 2021-05-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

许多电影人对《夺宝奇兵》赞赏有加，或称该片促使他们投身电影事业，如[[克里斯·卡特_(編劇)|克里斯·卡特]]<ref name="DOGLegacy" />、[[賽門·金柏格|賽門·金柏格]]、[[強·托特陶|強·托特陶]]<ref>{{cite web | first = Chris | last = Nashawaty | title = The golden Indiana Jones franchise | url = https://ew.com/article/2008/03/07/golden-indiana-jones-franchise/ | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2008-03-07 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210612235607/https://ew.com/article/2008/03/07/golden-indiana-jones-franchise/ | archive-date = 2021-06-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[丹·布朗|丹·布朗]]<ref name="InverseInfluences">{{cite web | first = Sean | last = Hutchinson | title = How 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' Helped Make The Marvel Cinematic Universe Possible | url = https://www.inverse.com/article/16916-how-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-helped-make-the-marvel-cinematic-universe-possible | website = Inverse | date = 2016-06-13 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126094957/https://www.inverse.com/article/16916-how-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-helped-make-the-marvel-cinematic-universe-possible | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、乔·庄斯顿。参与本片制作对庄斯顿导演《[[美國隊長_(電影)|美国队长]]》影响很大，特别是人物设计<ref name="ASCMag" /><ref name="DOGLegacy" />。导演[[史蒂文·索德伯格|史蒂文·索德伯格]]2014年推出本片黑白剪辑版，去除所有原版音效，旨在促使观众关注斯皮尔伯格的场面调度和剪辑<ref>{{cite web | first = Rob | last = Dean | title = Steven Soderbergh made a black-and-white version of Raiders of the Lost Ark | url = https://www.avclub.com/steven-soderbergh-made-a-black-and-white-version-of-rai-1798272357 | website = The A.V. Club | date = 2014-09-23 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201114082323/https://news.avclub.com/steven-soderbergh-made-a-black-and-white-version-of-rai-1798272357 | archive-date = 2020-11-14 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。2020年[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|冠状病毒病疫情]]期间，导演[[詹姆斯·岡恩|詹姆斯·岡恩]]推荐世人观看《夺宝奇兵》等动作片；《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》向读者推荐的35部电影也包括本片<ref name="IGNGunn">{{cite web | first = Matt | last = Fowler | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/james-gunn-recommends-54-action-movies-to-cure-the-quarantine-blues | title = James Gunn Recommends 54 Action Movies to Cure the Quarantine Blues | website = IGN | date = 2020-04-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210509163744/https://www.ign.com/articles/james-gunn-recommends-54-action-movies-to-cure-the-quarantine-blues | archive-date = 2021-05-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | first1 = Patrick | last1 = Smith | first2 = Helen | last2 = O'Hara | title = The 35 best films to stream during lockdown: from Raiders of the Lost Ark to City of God | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/best-movies-streaming-online-uk-b1794699.html | website = [[獨立報|The Independent]] | date = 2021-01-29 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610015359/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/best-movies-streaming-online-uk-b1794699.html | archive-date = 2021-06-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

本片对电影<ref name="WAPOInspirations">{{cite web | first = Jen | last = Chaney | title = The Spawn of Indy | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/artsandliving/movies/features/2008/indiana-jones/index.html | website = The Washington Post | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190925215157/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/artsandliving/movies/features/2008/indiana-jones/index.html | archive-date = 2019-09-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Schneider-2013">{{cite book | last = Schneider | first = Steven Jay | title = 1001 Movies You Must See Before You Die | url = https://archive.org/details/1001moviesyoumus0000unse_p9h4 | year = 2013 | chapter = 1980s | publisher = Murdoch Books Pty Limited | location = Boston, Massachusetts | isbn = 978-0-7641-6613-6}}</ref>、电视、电子游戏等传媒影响很大<ref name="InverseInfluences" /><ref name="WAPOInspirations" />。1982至1989年，密西西比州[[海泉市|海泉市]]儿童克里斯·斯特龙波洛斯、埃里克·扎拉、杰森·兰布制作本片的同名[[愛好者電影|业余翻拍电影]]《[[夺宝奇兵：改编版|夺宝奇兵：改编版]]》，斯皮尔伯格向三人祝贺<ref name="VanityFairAdaptation">{{cite web | url = https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2004/03/raiders200403 | title = Raiders of the Lost Backyard | first = Jim | last = Windolf | website = Vanity Fair | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126061911/https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2004/03/raiders200403 | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 时间的考验 ===
众多媒体把本片评为影史杰作<ref name="Empire500">{{cite web | title = The 500 Greatest Movies Of All Time | date = 2008-10-03 | website = [[帝國雜誌|Empire]] | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/500-greatest-movies/ | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709034225/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/500-greatest-movies/ | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="THRJun14">{{cite web | title = Hollywood's 100 Favorite Films | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/100-best-films-ever-hollywood-favorites-818512/ | date = 2014-06-25 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709034016/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/100-best-films-ever-hollywood-favorites-818512/ | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="LastingIGN">{{cite web | first = Jim | last = Vejvoda | title = The Top 25 Action Movies | access-date = 2021-07-11 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/01/10/the-top-25-action-movies | website = IGN | date = 2016-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210611002303/https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/01/10/the-top-25-action-movies | archive-date = 2021-06-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="ActionBFI">{{cite web | first = Matthew | last = Thrift | title = 10 best action movies | url = https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/news-bfi/lists/10-best-action-movies | date = 2015-07-02 | publisher = British Film Institute | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210509163913/https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/news-bfi/lists/10-best-action-movies | archive-date = 2021-05-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。埃伯特的《伟大电影》系列著作称本片特效仍不过时，对这类电影而言堪称完美。他称赞本片兴奋点看似漫不经心，娱乐效果却是高潮不断。<ref name="ebertGreatest" />[[英國電影協會|英國電影協會]]把本片列入史上十佳动作片，称影片的布局和兴奋点对于青少年男子而言无与伦比，同时还有印第安纳·琼斯最令人耳目一新的搭档：喝起酒来像汉子，聪明伶俐、风度翩翩的凯伦·阿兰<ref name="ActionBFI" />。2014年《好莱坞报道》向2120名娱乐业从业人员开展民意调查，《夺宝奇兵》排在史上最佳电影第十三位<ref name="THRJun14" />。影片在电影参考书《[[死前必看的1001部电影|死前必看的1001部电影]]》上同样榜上有名<ref name="Schneider-2013" />。

[[汇总媒体|评论汇总]]网站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]共收集本片84篇评论，认可度达九成五。网站的共识评述写道：“英勇的桥段、狡黠的幽默、令人紧张到指节发白的动作，《夺宝奇兵》是史上堪称完美的娱乐冒险片杰作。”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/raiders_of_the_lost_ark | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | publisher = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-07-04 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210704080911/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/raiders_of_the_lost_ark}}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据16篇评论为本片打分85（最高100），代表“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/raiders-of-the-lost-ark | title = Raiders of the Lost Ark | publisher = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309042613/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/raiders-of-the-lost-ark | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | access-date = 2021-07-11}}</ref>。2005年，[[美国编剧工会|美国编剧工会]]评选过去75年间最优秀的101部剧本，本片排名第42<ref>{{cite web | title = 101 Greatest Screenplays | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210625023636/https://www.wga.org/writers-room/101-best-lists/101-greatest-screenplays | url = https://www.wga.org/writers-room/101-best-lists/101-greatest-screenplays | publisher = Writers Guild of America West | year = 2005 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-06-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = 101 Greatest Screenplays | url = https://www.wga.org/writers-room/101-best-lists/101-greatest-screenplays/list | publisher = Writers Guild of America West | year = 2005 | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709040512/https://www.wga.org/writers-room/101-best-lists/101-greatest-screenplays/list | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。2008年《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》评选影史电影五百强，《夺宝奇兵》仅次于1972年的黑帮片《[[教父_(電影)|教父]]》位居第二，文章称赞影片娱乐效果远超其他冒险片<ref name="Empire500" />。1997年，[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]面向美国影史杰作评选[[AFI百年百大電影|AFI百年百大電影]]，本片排名第60；2007年再度评选[[AFI百年百大电影_(2007年版)|十周年版]]，本片排第66<ref>{{cite web | title = AFI's 100 Years... 100 Movies – 10th Anniversary Edition | format = PDF | url = https://prdaficalmjediwestussa.blob.core.windows.net/images/2019/08/100MoviesANNIVERSARY.pdf | publisher = [[美国电影学会|American Film Institute]] | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101004848/https://prdaficalmjediwestussa.blob.core.windows.net/images/2019/08/100MoviesANNIVERSARY.pdf | archive-date = 2020-11-01 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。2001年评选[[AFI百年百大驚悚電影|百年百大惊悚片]]，《夺宝奇兵》排第十<ref>{{cite web | title = AFI's 100 Years...100 Thrills | url = https://www.afi.com/afis-100-years-100-thrills/ | publisher = American Film Institute | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210710222459/https://www.afi.com/afis-100-years-100-thrills/ | archive-date = 2021-07-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>；2003年评选[[AFI百年百大英雄與反派|百大银幕英雄与恶魔]]，印第安纳·琼斯在英雄榜排第二，仅次于《[[怪屋疑雲|怪屋疑雲]]》（1962年）里的[[阿提克斯·芬奇|阿提克斯·芬奇]]<ref name="AFIHeroes">{{cite web | title = Afi's 100 Years...100 Heroes & Villains | url = https://www.afi.com/afis-100-years-100-heroes-villians/ | publisher = American Film Institute | access-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709205215/https://www.afi.com/afis-100-years-100-heroes-villians/ | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

