3 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first1 = Tim | last1 = Robey | first2 = Robbie | last2 = Collin | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/0/best-action-movies-ever-made/11-raiders-lost-ark-1981/ | title = Beat it, Kingsman: the 24 greatest action movies of all time | website = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2017-09-21 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201122074227/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/0/best-action-movies-ever-made/11-raiders-lost-ark-1981/ | archive-date = 2020-11-22 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，《Time Out》2020年评选再度上榜但不分先后<ref>{{cite web | first = Joshua | last = Rothkopf | title = The 101 best action movies ever made | url = https://www.timeout.com/film/the-101-best-action-movies-ever-made | website = Time Out | date = 2020-08-14 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210707183939/https://www.timeout.com/film/the-101-best-action-movies-ever-made | archive-date = 2021-07-07 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。IGN把本片评为20世纪80年代最佳动作片<ref>{{cite web | first = William | last = Bibbiani | title = The 10 Best '80s Action Movies | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/07/26/the-10-best-80s-action-movies | website = IGN | date = 2018-07-27 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210707135114/https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/07/26/the-10-best-80s-action-movies | archive-date = 2021-07-07 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，烂番茄和《[[时尚先生_(刊物)|时尚先生]]》都把本片列为冒险片杰作<ref>{{cite web | first = Emma | last = Carey | title = The Best Adventure Movies of All Time To Set Off into the Great Unknown | url = https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/g32779509/best-adventure-movies/ | website = [[时尚先生_(刊物)|Esquire]] | date = 2020-06-06 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210301232415/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/g32779509/best-adventure-movies/ | archive-date = 2021-03-01 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Best Adventure Movies Of All Time | url = https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/50-best-adventure-movies-of-all-time/5/ | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180129000442/http://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/50-best-adventure-movies-of-all-time/5/ | archive-date = 2018-01-29 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2005年，英国[[第四台_(英國)|第四台]]观众投票把《夺宝奇兵》排在史上最佳家庭片第二十<ref>{{cite web | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4553694.stm | title = ET Crowned 'Greatest Family Film' | date = 2005-12-23 | publisher = BBC News Online | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200227211556/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4553694.stm | archive-date = 2020-02-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2021年，《帝国杂志》读者在评选史上佳片时把本片排第七<ref>{{cite web | title = The 100 Greatest Movies | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/best-movies-2/ | website = Empire | date = 2021-03-24 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709185426/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/best-movies-2/ | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。另据《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》消息，[[互联网电影资料库|互联网电影资料库]]、烂番茄用户投票结合专业评分把《夺宝奇兵》排在影史佳片第十六<ref>{{cite web | first = Charles | last = Stockdale | title = Let the debate begin: 50 best movies of all time | url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/money/2017/12/22/let-debate-begin-50-best-movies-all-time/869073001/ | website = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | date = 2019-12-15 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109043555/https://eu.usatoday.com/story/money/2017/12/22/let-debate-begin-50-best-movies-all-time/869073001/ | archive-date = 2020-11-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》读者投票将本片评为史上最佳暑期大片，超过《大白鲨》和《[[異形_(電影)|异形]]》（1979年）<ref>{{cite web | first = Justin | last = Chang | url = https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-08-20/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-jaws-ultimate-summer-movie-showdown-stand-by-me-final | title = How 'Raiders of the Lost Ark' beat 'Jaws' – and won the Ultimate Summer Movie Showdown | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 2020-08-20 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210710035030/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-08-20/raiders-of-the-lost-ark-jaws-ultimate-summer-movie-showdown-stand-by-me-final | archive-date = 2021-07-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2013年，情景喜剧《[[生活大爆炸|生活大爆炸]]》[[生活大爆炸_(第七季)|第七季]]某分集台词宣称，琼斯在《夺宝奇兵》一事无成，纳粹无论如何都会找到约柜，打开后全部惨死，琼斯的行动根本没有影响。马特·波姆罗伊在《时尚先生》发文同意上述看法，只是玛丽昂十有八九会死于托赫特之手，约柜很可能用飞翼运到德国，希特勒打开后丧命。琼斯的干扰确保约柜落入美国人之手，可能打开约柜的德国人反而逃过一劫。<ref>{{cite web | first = Matt | last = Pomroy | url = https://www.esquireme.com/brief/indiana-jones-hypothesis | title = The Indiana Jones Hypothesis | website = Esquire | date = 2014-08-13 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210703174949/https://www.esquireme.com/brief/indiana-jones-hypothesis | archive-date = 2021-07-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Oliver | last = Sava | title = The Big Bang Theory: "The Raiders Minimization" | url = https://www.avclub.com/the-big-bang-theory-the-raiders-minimization-1798178275 | website = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]] | date = 2013-10-10 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191103085020/https://tv.avclub.com/the-big-bang-theory-the-raiders-minimization-1798178275 | archive-date = 2019-11-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 前传、续集、改编 ==
{{main|夺宝奇兵{{!}}-{zh-cn:夺宝奇兵系列; zh-hk:奪寶奇兵系列; zh-tw:印第安納瓊斯系列;}-}}
[[File:Sean_Connery_(1983).jpg|thumb]]（摄于1983年）在《[[聖戰奇兵|聖戰奇兵]]》扮演印第安纳·琼斯之父亨利]]

《夺宝奇兵》的热卖催生两部续集、一部前传，原作上映期间《魔宮傳奇》就于1982年进入开发阶段<ref>{{cite news | first = Leslie | last = Wayne | title = Hollywood Sequels Are Just The Ticket | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1982/07/18/business/hollywood-sequels-are-just-the-ticket.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1982-07-18 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | page = 31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120321/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/07/18/business/hollywood-sequels-are-just-the-ticket.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。该片是《夺宝奇兵》的前传，讲述琼斯为印度村庄居民寻找圣石，同时解放残暴邪教首脑控制的奴隶。影片同样根据卢卡斯的构想编剧，斯皮尔伯格导演，福特回归扮演琼斯。电影上映后打破多项票房纪录，是1984年美国本土票房最高的电影，但评价不及原作，影评人批评片中种族立场和[[女性贬抑|厌女]]倾向。<ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Indiana Jones' Topping 'Jedi' Box-office Record | page = C17 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/30/movies/indiana-jones-topping-jedi-box-office-record.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1984-05-30 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120324/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/30/movies/indiana-jones-topping-jedi-box-office-record.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = James | last = Charisma | title = 'Indiana Jones' Has Aged Terribly | website = [[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] | date = 2020-06-19 | url = https://www.vice.com/en/article/j5wnay/indiana-jones-has-aged-terribly | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417005816/https://www.vice.com/en/article/j5wnay/indiana-jones-has-aged-terribly | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = 'Indiana Jones' Stirs Ratings Debate | page = C12 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/21/movies/indiana-jones-stirs-ratings-debate.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1984-05-21 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120327/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/05/21/movies/indiana-jones-stirs-ratings-debate.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

1989年，《夺宝奇兵》续集《[[聖戰奇兵|聖戰奇兵]]》问世，是原版三部曲收宫之作<ref name="SequelLastCrusade">{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Indiana Jones Conquers Box-Office Competition | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1989/05/31/movies/indiana-jones-conquers-box-office-competition.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1989-05-31 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | page = C20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411120335/https://www.nytimes.com/1989/05/31/movies/indiana-jones-conquers-box-office-competition.html | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="SequelLastCrusadeOral">{{cite web | title = The Making Of Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/indiana-jones-making-last-crusade/ | website = Empire | date = 2012-10-08 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510094957/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/indiana-jones-making-last-crusade/ | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。琼斯在片中踏上找寻[[圣杯|圣杯]]的冒险之旅，路上还有父亲亨利（[[肖恩·康纳利|肖恩·康纳利]]饰）参与<ref name="SequelLastCrusadeOral" />。《圣战奇兵》同样刷新票房纪录，在年度票房榜名列前茅并获影评人好评<ref name="SequelLastCrusade" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Hollywood Registers A Bonanza For 1989 | page = C17 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/01/04/movies/hollywood-registers-a-bonanza-for-1989.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-01-04 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210517181330/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/01/04/movies/hollywood-registers-a-bonanza-for-1989.html | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。斯皮尔伯格表示，《圣战奇兵》一定程度上是他为《魔宮傳奇》反响不佳致歉<ref>{{cite web | first = Simon | last = Brew | title = Revisiting Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/revisiting-indiana-jones-and-the-last-crusade/ | publisher = Den of Geek | date = 2014-01-30 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210417231121/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/revisiting-indiana-jones-and-the-last-crusade/ | archive-date = 2021-04-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。卢卡斯此后开创电视剧项目，《[[少年印第安那瓊斯年譜|少年印第安那瓊斯年譜]]》1992年开播，乔治·霍尔扮演老年琼斯回忆年青时的征程，福特、[[西恩·派翠克·福納瑞|西恩·派翠克·福納瑞]]、科里·凯里尔分别诠释不同年龄段的琼斯<ref>{{cite web | first = Ken | last = Tucker | title = The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles | url = https://ew.com/article/1992/02/28/young-indiana-jones-chronicles/ | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 1992-02-28 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227045015/https://ew.com/article/1992/02/28/young-indiana-jones-chronicles/ | archive-date = 2021-02-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2008年，印第安纳·琼斯系列第四弹《[[印第安納瓊斯：水晶骷髏王國|印第安納瓊斯：水晶骷髏王國]]》面世，阿兰在片中回归饰演玛丽昂，[[西亞·李畢福|西亞·李畢福]]扮演玛丽昂与琼斯的儿子穆特·威廉姆斯。电影背景改为20世纪50年代，琼斯的对手变成苏联人，目标是找到水晶骷髅<ref name="SequelSyFy">{{cite web | first = Will | last = Leitch | title = This Week in Genre History: Indiana Jones And The Kingdom Of The Crystal Skull Nukes The Fridge | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/indiana-jones-and-the-kingdom-of-the-crystal-skull-history | publisher = Syfy | date = 2020-05-20 | access-date = 2021-07-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116190423/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/indiana-jones-and-the-kingdom-of-the-crystal-skull-history | archive-date = 2021-01-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。影片票房热卖，但影评人和影迷反响两极分化<ref name="SequelSyFy" /><ref name="EWSequelCrystal">{{cite web | first1 = Darren | last1 = Franich | first2 = Chris | last2 = Nashawaty | title = Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull: A critical conversation | url = https://ew.com/movies/2018/05/22/indiana-jones-and-the-kingdom-of-the-crystal-skull-turns-10/ | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2018-05-22 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200709074418/https://ew.com/movies/2018/05/22/indiana-jones-and-the-kingdom-of-the-crystal-skull-turns-10/ | archive-date = 2020-07-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Vinnie | last = Mancuso | title = The Opening of 'Kingdom of the Crystal Skull' Makes the Perfect Old Man Indiana Jones Movie | url = https://collider.com/indiana-jones-kingdom-of-the-crystal-skull-opening-scene-is-good/ | publisher = [[Collider|Collider]] | date = 2020-05-22 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200614185641/https://collider.com/indiana-jones-kingdom-of-the-crystal-skull-opening-scene-is-good/ | archive-date = 2020-06-14 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。卢卡斯与斯皮尔伯格像当年对待《魔宮傳奇》一样为影片辩护，同时为新作反响不佳致歉<ref name="SequelSyFy" /><ref name="EWSequelCrystal" />。本系列[[印第安納瓊斯5|第五部电影]]计划2022年7月上映，[[詹姆斯·曼高德|詹姆斯·曼高德]]执导，福特、[[菲比·沃勒-布里奇|菲比·沃勒-布里奇]]、[[麦斯·米科尔森|麦斯·米科尔森]]主演<ref>{{cite web | first = Justin | last = Kroll | title = 'Indiana Jones 5': Mads Mikkelsen Joins Harrison Ford And Phoebe Waller-Bridge in Sequel | url = https://deadline.com/2021/04/indiana-jones-5-mads-mikkelsen-joins-harrison-ford-and-phoebe-waller-bridge-in-sequel-1234732751/ | website = [[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] | date = 2021-04-15 | access-date = 2021-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210705125213/https://deadline.com/2021/04/indiana-jones-5-mads-mikkelsen-joins-harrison-ford-and-phoebe-waller-bridge-in-sequel-1234732751/ | archive-date = 2021-07-05 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

众多小说、漫画、电子游戏围绕印第安纳·琼斯及各电影配角展开，详细介绍他们的历险和其他经历<ref name="RaidersVideoGame" /><ref name="CBRComicBooks" /><ref>{{cite web | title = The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles #8 | url = https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/92-150/The-Young-Indiana-Jones-Chronicles-8 | publisher = [[黑马漫画|Dark Horse Comics]] | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308105545/https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/92-150/The-Young-Indiana-Jones-Chronicles-8 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="EmpireNovels">{{cite web | first = Owen | last = Williams | title = The Indiana Jones Novels | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/indiana-jones-novels/ | website = Empire | date = 2012-10-10 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210420181605/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/indiana-jones-novels/ | archive-date = 2021-04-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这些作品背景横跨全球，有些发生在电影情节之前，有些在以后，描绘琼斯的第一次婚姻，搜寻[[印第安纳·琼斯与命运之矛|命运之矛]]、[[印第安纳·琼斯与巨人之舞|梅林]]、巴别塔中的地狱机器、[[释迦牟尼|佛佗]]圣约<ref name="ScreenRantNovelsGames">{{cite web | last = Andersen | first = Andy | title = 15 Best Indiana Jones Stories Outside The Movies | url = https://screenrant.com/best-indiana-jones-stories-not-movies-comics-books-tv-show/ | website = Screen Rant | date = 2017-06-06 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210422212242/https://screenrant.com/best-indiana-jones-stories-not-movies-comics-books-tv-show/ | archive-date = 2021-04-22 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[印第安纳琼斯与王之杖|摩西的权杖]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Reed | first = Kristan | title = Indiana Jones and the Staff Of Kings | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/indiana-jones-and-the-staff-of-kings-review | website = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | date = 2009-06-15  | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210424160553/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/indiana-jones-and-the-staff-of-kings-review | archive-date = 2021-04-24 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[印第安纳·琼斯与贤者之石|贤者之石]]、恐龙、独角兽的角、[[印第安纳·琼斯与德尔斐的劫难|德尔斐神谕]]等历险，探索[[斯芬克斯|斯芬克斯]]、[[挪亚方舟|挪亚方舟]]、[[亞特蘭提斯之謎|亚特兰蒂斯]]的秘密<ref name="IGNNovelsGames">{{cite web | last = Chitwood | first = Scott | title = The Lost Adventures Of Indiana Jones | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/02/23/the-lost-adventures-of-indiana-jones | website = IGN | date = 2000-02-23 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210421095706/https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/02/23/the-lost-adventures-of-indiana-jones | archive-date = 2021-04-21 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="ScreenRantNovelsGames" /><ref>{{cite web | last = Andersen | first = Andy | title = The Indiana Jones Novels | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/indiana-jones-novels/ | website = Empire | date = 2012-10-10 | access-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210420181605/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/indiana-jones-novels/ | archive-date = 2021-04-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。琼斯有时还会遇到贝洛克等反派的阻挠，获萨拉赫等人帮助<ref name="ScreenRantNovelsGames" /><ref name="IGNNovelsGames" />。

